column1: # Name: Political Stability and Absence of Violence/Terrorism (Worldwide Governance Indicator)

# Definition: Reflects perceptions of the likelihood that the government will be destabilized or overthrown by unconstitutional or violent means, including politically-motivated violence and terrorism. Estimate of governance (ranges from approximately -2.5 (weak) to 2.5 (strong) governance performance)
# Data from the No Ceilings project: http://noceilings.org
# For more about the data, please visit http://noceilings.org/data
